Danièle Parola https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dani%C3%A8le_Parola 0 Danièle Parola (March 28, 1905 – September 2, 1998) was a French film actress. She starred in the 1932 crime film Narcotics. She was married to the actor and producer André Daven. Danièle_Parola ( March_28_,_1905 – September_2_,_1998 ) was a_French_film_actress . She starred in the_1932_crime_film_Narcotics .
